# === ROOT DIRECTORY PROTECTION ===
# Prevent common file organization mistakes
# (These patterns catch files that should be in subdirectories)

# Session/task artifacts (should be in docs/maintenance/)
/*_analysis.md
/*_report.md
/*_completion.md
/*_walkthrough.md
/*_summary.md

# Debug/test files (should be in tests/ or workspace/)
/debug_*.py
/test_*.py
/debug_*.sh
/test_*.sh

# Results files (should be in tests/<feature>/results/)
/results_*.json
/results_*.md
/RESULTS_*.md

# Research data (should be in tests/experiments/)
/research_*.json
/research_*.md

# Exceptions: Legitimate root files
!README.md
!CHANGELOG.md
!CRITICAL_INFO.md
!CONTRIBUTING.md
!LICENSE
!HowToRunMe.md
!VERIFICATION_GUIDE.md
